        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Regulation Through Litigation Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill modifies the authority of federal agencies to enter into consent decrees and limits the inclusion of attorney fees in consent decrees or settlement agreements that result in a regulation or guidance document.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
